text: The White Shadow is a 1923 British drama movie directed by Graham Cutts and Alfred Hitchcock and was based on a play. It stars Betty Compson, Henry Victor, Clive Brook, Daisy Campbell, Olaf Hytten and was rediscovered in 2011 in New Zealand. ==Other websites== * * Category:1923 drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:British silent movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by Graham Cutts Category:Movies directed by Alfred Hitchcock Category:Movies set in London
